quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  62,1,"Kala ko woni nder kammuuji e leydi hino seninnde Allah, Laam…óo, cenii…óo, Poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo on."
  62,2,"Ko KaŇčko nuli e humammbinnee…ďe …ďeen Nulaa…óo jiyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, himo janngana …ďe Aayeeje makko …óen, o la…ď…ďina …ďe, o anndina …ďe deftere nden e Sunna on, hay si tawiino ko adii …óuum, …ďe laatino e majjere …ďanngude."
  62,3,"(O nuli mo) kadi e wo…ó…ďe goo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe hawrondiraali e …ďeen taho. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo on."
  62,4,"∆äuum ko …ďural Allah, Homo okka ngal mo o muuyani. Allah ko Jom …ďural mawnngal."
  62,5,"Misal ronndinaa…ďe Tawreeta …ďeen refti …ďe nigolliraali nde, no wa'i wa mbabba ronndii mba defte. Yeru yim…ďe yeddoo…ďe aayeeje Alla …óeen bonii. Allah feewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."
  62,6,"Maaku: ""Ko onon yo HuudiŇčkoo…ďe ! Si on aa∆īike wonan'de ko on yi…óaa…ďe Allah ko wanaa yim…ďe heddii…ďe …ďen, haray njelee maayde, si tawii ko on ngoongu…ďe""."
  62,7,"∆Āe njelotaako nde muk, sabu ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ngardini kon. Allah ko ganndu…óo too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."
  62,8,"Maaku: ""Ndee maayde nde ndogoton, pellet, ko nde hawraynde e mon. Refti ndutte…óon to oon ganndu…óo ko wirnii e ko fee√Īi, O kumpita on ko ngollayno…óon kon""."
  62,9,"Ko onon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe ! Si juulde nden noddinanaama √Īalnde Juma, njaccee e jaŇčtagol Allah, ngacciton njeengu. Ko …óuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on, si tawno ko on anndu…ďe !"
  62,10,"Si juulde nden gasii, haray ca,akitee ka leydi, …óa…ď…ďon …ďural Allah ngal [woni arsike], jaŇčtoron innde Allah ko …óuu…ói, mbelajo'o on maloyte."
  62,11,"Si …ďe nji'ii njeeyngu maa fijindaaru, …ďe hammira toon, …ďe ngaccama hi…óa darii. Maaku: ""Ko ko woni ka Allah kon …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude belee…óe e njulaaku. Ko Allah …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e arsikoo…ďe …ďeen""."
